svg.desc:
Animated diagram showing the seven major automation steps performed
        by the CAP Operator during application deployment:
        1) Istio Gateway created; 2) DNS + TLS provisioned via Gardener;
        3) Content Deployment jobs push UIs and destinations into SAP BTP;
        4) Approuter, CAP Server and other Deployments rolled out; 5) Tenant
        Operation job runs (provisioning / upgrade / deprovisioning);
        6) Virtual Service created last, exposing tenant routes;
        7) Scheduled Routines run continuously — rollout on credential
        rotation and version cleanup driven by Prometheus.
